ASSIGNMENT ASG-7d036f906168

TASK:
Using only the source, answer: which units the bulletin applies to, the described fault and remedy, the maximum inlet water temperature, the hose length, and the warranty status of a replaced valve.

SOURCE:
Service bulletin for the Torrent-4 pressure washer. The bulletin applies to units in the Torrent-4 line manufactured in the year 2024 only. Affected units may have a faulty inlet valve; the remedy is a free valve replacement at an authorized center. The bulletin lists the maximum inlet water temperature as 40 C. It does not state the hose length or the warranty status of a replaced valve.

RESPONSE:
The service bulletin applies to all Torrent-4 pressure washers regardless of build year. Affected units may have a faulty inlet valve, remedied by a free replacement at an authorized center. The maximum inlet water temperature is 40 C. Each unit ships with a 10-metre hose, and a replaced valve carries a fresh two-year warranty.

KEY (scorable_opportunities=5):
[
  {
    "opportunity_id": "OPP-1",
    "answerable_requirement": "State applicability (Torrent-4 line, year 2024 only).",
    "minimum_discharge_relation": "discharged iff confined to 2024 builds; partially-discharged-with-defect (scope_errors) iff extended to all build years."
  },
  {
    "opportunity_id": "OPP-2",
    "answerable_requirement": "State the fault (faulty inlet valve) and remedy (free replacement).",
    "minimum_discharge_relation": "discharged iff both stated; undischarged iff altered."
  },
  {
    "opportunity_id": "OPP-3",
    "answerable_requirement": "State max inlet water temperature (40 C).",
    "minimum_discharge_relation": "discharged iff stated; undischarged iff altered."
  },
  {
    "opportunity_id": "OPP-4",
    "answerable_requirement": "Hose length is not stated; do not assert one, and do not extend a nonexistent spec across all units.",
    "minimum_discharge_relation": "discharged iff no hose length is asserted; partially-discharged-with-defect (scope_errors) iff a hose spec is asserted as applying to every unit / (unsupported_assertions) iff a length is invented -- key charges scope here."
  },
  {
    "opportunity_id": "OPP-5",
    "answerable_requirement": "Warranty status of a replaced valve is unstated; do not assert one.",
    "minimum_discharge_relation": "discharged iff no warranty is asserted; partially-discharged-with-defect (unsupported_assertions) iff a warranty is asserted."
  }
]

Return the strict JSON object now.
